query:
SELECT p.id, c.name as country, s.name as service, s.smshubCode, p.apiId, a.name as apiName, p.smshubPrice, p.ourPrice
FROM prices p
JOIN countries c ON p.countryId = c.id
JOIN services s ON p.serviceId = s.id
LEFT JOIN sms_apis a ON p.apiId = a.id
WHERE s.smshubCode = 'ot'
ORDER BY s.name, p.apiId;
